Package gov.usgs.volcanoes.core.legacy.plot.transform

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Transformer
    An interface for an object that can perform a translation from user unit-space (cm, microradians, lat/lon, etc) to pixel-space on a Plot.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArbDepthCalculator
    A class used to help plot hypocenters by projecting them onto a line drawn between 2 arbitrary points on the earth
    IdentityTransformer
    A basic implementation of Transformer which returns exactly what it is passed.
